text: Prince Sanggye (January 21, 1769 - November 20, 1786) or Crown Prince Wanpung was a royal family member of the Joseon dynasty in Korea. He was the first son of Prince Eunjeon.9회 원아웃에 교체된 '사도세자 라인' Ohmynews 2008.04.17. Euneon was a illegitimate son of Crown Prince Sado.
